<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>My First Website</title>
    <style>
        /* Base Styles */
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f6f8;
            color: #333;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
        }

        /* Header Style (Green Section from Screenshot) */
        header {
            background-color: #04aa6d; /* The exact W3Schools green style */
            color: white;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        header h1 {
            margin: 0 0 10px 0;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
        }

        header p {
            margin: 0;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        /* Main Content Container */
        main {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            padding: 20px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        /* Section Cards (About Me & Projects) */
        section {
            background: white;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }

        section h2 {
            color: #04aa6d;
            margin-top: 0;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #f4f6f8;
            padding-bottom: 8px;
        }

        /* Projects List */
        ul {
            padding-left: 20px;
        }

        li {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: #555;
        }

        /* Footer Style */
        footer {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            color: #777;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <h1>Hello, LinkedIn!</h1>
        <p>This site is built with HTML and CSS.</p>
    </header>

    <main>
        <section>
            <h2>About Me</h2>
            <p>I am sharpening my web development skills. This is my very first webpage in a long time, and I am excitingly deepening my HTML & CSS foundations to grow as a developer.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Projects</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Portfolio landing page</li>
                <li>Product showcase</li>
                <li>Responsive blog layout</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <p>Built with ♥ using HTML & CSS.</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>

